com.spotify.sdk.android.playback

Interface NativePlayer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NativeSdkPlayer

    public interface NativePlayer
    Any native player that connects to Spotify playback services must implement this interface. It can also be used to mock native player for test purposes.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  NativePlayer.AudioDeliveredCallback
      Interface used to register callback for audio data received from native player.
      static interface  NativePlayer.AudioFlushCallback
      Interface used to register callback for audio flush command received from native player.

      • playUri

        void playUri(String uri)
      throws NativeSpotifyException
        Plays a single uri. Which uris are supported depends on a specific implementation of the native player.
        Parameters:
        uri - Uri to play with the player.
        Throws:
        NativeSpotifyException - Thrown when playback fails. Note: not all playback errors have to be immediate. For details refer to specific implementation.

      • playUri

        void playUri(String uri,
             int index,
             int positionInMs)
      throws NativeSpotifyException
        Plays a single uri from specified index and specified position. Which uris are supported depends on a specific implementation of the native player.
        Parameters:
        uri - Uri to play with the player.
        index - A zero-based index from which to play.
        positionInMs - A position to start playback from.
        Throws:
        NativeSpotifyException - Thrown when playback fails. Note: not all playback errors have to be immediate. For details refer to specific implementation.

      • playTrackList

        void playTrackList(String[] trackUris)
            throws NativeSpotifyException
        Plays a list of uris. Only track uris are supported in this case. Trying to play list of album or playlists uris will not work.
        Parameters:
        trackUris - The list of tracks to play.
        Throws:
        NativeSpotifyException - Thrown when playback fails. Note: not all playback errors have to be immediate. For details refer to specific implementation.

      • playTrackList

        Parameters:

      • queue

        void queue(String trackUri)
    throws NativeSpotifyException
        Queue the track. When track is queued it will be played directly after the one that is currently playing.
        Parameters:
        trackUri - The uri of the track to queue.
        Throws:
        NativeSpotifyException - Thrown when queuing fails.

      • clearQueue

        void clearQueue()
         throws NativeSpotifyException
        Clears the queue. This will remove all tracks remaining in the queue but it will not affect currently playing track.
        Throws:
        NativeSpotifyException - Thrown when clearing the queue fails.
